Use @Chili Lime Butter{3.5%ounce} and enjoy.

> Everything's better with butter. This mildly spicy, tangy accompaniment is guaranteed
> to make all your grilled goodies taste 100x better. Use to top your Surf & Turf Pack,
> slather over corn on the cob, or simply stock up and keep in your fridge for an
> instant upgrade to any meal. You can't go wrong.